posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Vintage', 'Come discover Vintage living in Pleasanton, CA.', 'A contemporary community of of upscale apartments and townhomes that is as much an escape as it is a destination.', 'A place where beautifully appointed residences, resort-style amenities, rolling lawns and parks, and boutique shops come together to create a distinctly new leisure lifestyle.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 10', 'OR Text', '10', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1098 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Stackable Washer & Dryer', '- Walk-in Closet*', '- Wood-style Flooring', '- Quartz Countertops', '- Deep soaking tubs and tiled showers *', '- Balcony/Patio/Terrace*', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '*Select apartments', 'Community Amenities', '- Outdoor social veranda', '- Pet Spa', '- Billiards/Game Room', '- On-Site Retail', '- State-of-the-Art Fitness Center', '- Resort pool and spa terrace', '- Vintage greens game lawn', '- Bike storage and workshop', '- Yoga and pilates studio', '- Lobby Lounge & Coffee Bar', '- Sophisticated resident clubhouse', '- Demonstration Kitchen', '- Wi-Fi lounge and work center', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Tuesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Wednesday: 9:00AM-7:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sunday: 12:00PM-5:00PM', 'Vintage', '50 Vintage Circle, Pleasanton, CA, 94566', 'j4mH018W']
